---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Solutions | Intellica" description="Enterprise data & AI solutions ‚Äî from modern data platforms and analytics to production-grade AI systems.">

  <!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label anim-fade-up">Solutions & Services</div>
      <h1 class="anim-fade-up">Enterprise <span class="grad-text">Solutions</span></h1>
      <p class="anim-fade-up">Capabilities, services and AI portfolio designed for enterprise-scale data & AI transformation.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CAPABILITIES -->
  <section class="section section--white" id="capabilities">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center anim-fade-up">
        <div class="section-label" style="margin-inline:auto;">What We Do</div>
        <h2 class="section-title" style="color:var(--clr-light-text);">Core <span class="grad-text">Capabilities</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub">End-to-end data & AI competencies that we bring to every engagement.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-3 anim-fade-up">
        <div class="solution-card">
          <div class="icon-box"><span>üìä</span></div>
          <h3 style="color:var(--clr-light-text);">Modern Data Platforms</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--clr-light-muted);">Cloud-native data platform architecture, DWH modernization, data lake and lakehouse implementations across all major cloud providers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="solution-card">
          <div class="icon-box"><span>üìà</span></div>
          <h3 style="color:var(--clr-light-text);">BI & Advanced Analytics</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--clr-light-muted);">Enterprise dashboarding, self-service analytics, semantic layer design and KPI governance for data-driven decisions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="solution-card">
          <div class="icon-box"><span>ü§ñ</span></div>
          <h3 style="color:var(--clr-light-text);">AI & Machine Learning</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--clr-light-muted);">GenAI, LLM integration, predictive models, NLP and computer vision solutions ‚Äî from PoC to production with MLOps.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="solution-card">
          <div class="icon-box"><span>üîí</span></div>
          <h3 style="color:var(--clr-light-text);">Data Governance</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--clr-light-muted);">Data quality, lineage, cataloging, master data management and regulatory compliance frameworks for enterprises.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="solution-card">
          <div class="icon-box"><span>üîó</span></div>
          <h3 style="color:var(--clr-light-text);">Data Integration</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--clr-light-muted);">ETL/ELT orchestration, real-time streaming, data mesh patterns and observability for reliable data pipelines.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="solution-card">
          <div class="icon-box"><span>üéØ</span></div>
          <h3 style="color:var(--clr-light-text);">Consulting & Managed Services</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--clr-light-muted);">Strategy workshops, GAP analysis, architecture assessments, team augmentation and end-to-end managed services.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICES -->
  <section class="section section--light" id="services">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center anim-fade-up">
        <div class="section-label" style="margin-inline:auto;">Services</div>
        <h2 class="section-title" style="color:var(--clr-light-text);">How We <span class="grad-text">Deliver</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub">Engagement models and service areas tailored to your organization's needs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-2 anim-fade-up" style="gap:32px;">
        <div class="card-light service-card">
          <h3 style="color:var(--clr-light-text);margin-bottom:16px;">üèóÔ∏è Project Delivery</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--clr-light-muted);margin-bottom:16px;">Fixed-scope projects with clear milestones, deliverables and acceptance criteria. From architecture design to production deployment.</p>
          <ul class="service-list">
            <li>DWH/Data Platform Build</li>
            <li>BI & Analytics Implementation</li>
            <li>AI/ML Model Development</li>
            <li>Data Migration & Modernization</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card-light service-card">
          <h3 style="color:var(--clr-light-text);margin-bottom:16px;">‚öôÔ∏è Managed Services</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--clr-light-muted);margin-bottom:16px;">Ongoing operational support with SLA-driven service levels. We operate, monitor and continuously improve your data infrastructure.</p>
          <ul class="service-list">
            <li>Platform Operations & Maintenance</li>
            <li>Data Quality Monitoring</li>
            <li>Performance Optimization</li>
            <li>Expert Team Augmentation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card-light service-card">
          <h3 style="color:var(--clr-light-text);margin-bottom:16px;">üó∫Ô∏è Strategy & Advisory</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--clr-light-muted);margin-bottom:16px;">Strategic advisory services to define your data & AI vision, assess current state and build actionable roadmaps.</p>
          <ul class="service-list">
            <li>Data Strategy Workshops</li>
            <li>Architecture Assessment</li>
            <li>Technology Selection</li>
            <li>Governance Framework Design</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card-light service-card">
          <h3 style="color:var(--clr-light-text);margin-bottom:16px;">üéì Training & Enablement</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--clr-light-muted);margin-bottom:16px;">Knowledge transfer and capability building to ensure your teams can independently operate and evolve the solutions we build together.</p>
          <ul class="service-list">
            <li>Technical Training Programs</li>
            <li>Hands-on Workshops</li>
            <li>Best Practice Documentation</li>
            <li>Ongoing Coaching & Support</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- AI PORTFOLIO -->
  <section class="section section--white" id="ai-portfolio">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center anim-fade-up">
        <div class="section-label" style="margin-inline:auto;">AI Portfolio</div>
        <h2 class="section-title" style="color:var(--clr-light-text);">Enterprise <span class="grad-text">AI Solutions</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub">Production-grade AI scenarios deployed across banking, telecom, manufacturing and retail enterprises.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-3 anim-fade-up">
        <div class="ai-portfolio-card card-light">
          <div class="ai-portfolio-card__badge">Conversational AI</div>
          <h3 style="color:var(--clr-light-text);">Talk To Your Data</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--clr-light-muted);">Natural language interface to enterprise databases. No SQL required ‚Äî governed, auditable, production-ready.</p>
          <div class="product-card__tags"><span class="tag tag-ai">GenAI</span><span class="tag tag-data">NL2SQL</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="ai-portfolio-card card-light">
          <div class="ai-portfolio-card__badge">Customer Intelligence</div>
          <h3 style="color:var(--clr-light-text);">Customer 360</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--clr-light-muted);">AI-powered unified customer view with next best action, cross-sell and churn prediction capabilities.</p>
          <div class="product-card__tags"><span class="tag tag-ai">Agentic AI</span><span class="tag tag-data">CRM</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="ai-portfolio-card card-light">
          <div class="ai-portfolio-card__badge">Demand Intelligence</div>
          <h3 style="color:var(--clr-light-text);">Demand Prediction</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--clr-light-muted);">ML-powered demand forecasting with seasonality, external factors and supply chain optimization.</p>
          <div class="product-card__tags"><span class="tag tag-ai">ML/DL</span><span class="tag tag-data">Forecasting</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="ai-portfolio-card card-light">
          <div class="ai-portfolio-card__badge">Knowledge AI</div>
          <h3 style="color:var(--clr-light-text);">Document Answers</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--clr-light-muted);">RAG-powered enterprise document assistant ‚Äî source-grounded, context-aware answers from internal knowledge bases.</p>
          <div class="product-card__tags"><span class="tag tag-ai">RAG</span><span class="tag tag-security">Governed</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="ai-portfolio-card card-light">
          <div class="ai-portfolio-card__badge">Code Intelligence</div>
          <h3 style="color:var(--clr-light-text);">AI Defect Solver</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--clr-light-muted);">Analyzes codebases, diagnoses bugs and suggests fixes ‚Äî agentic AI for software engineering teams.</p>
          <div class="product-card__tags"><span class="tag tag-ai">Agentic AI</span><span class="tag tag-data">DevOps</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="ai-portfolio-card card-light">
          <div class="ai-portfolio-card__badge">Industrial AI</div>
          <h3 style="color:var(--clr-light-text);">Predictive Maintenance</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--clr-light-muted);">Sensor-driven failure prediction for manufacturing ‚Äî minimize unplanned downtime and optimize throughput.</p>
          <div class="product-card__tags"><span class="tag tag-ai">IoT</span><span class="tag tag-security">Industry 4.0</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DWH Section -->
  <section class="section section--light" id="dwh">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center anim-fade-up">
        <div class="section-label" style="margin-inline:auto;">Data Platforms</div>
        <h2 class="section-title" style="color:var(--clr-light-text);">Data Platform <span class="grad-text">Transformation</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub">End-to-end DWH modernization, cloud migration and data operations expertise.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-3 anim-fade-up">
        <div class="dwh-card" style="background:linear-gradient(145deg,#F0FDF9,#EFF6FF);border:1px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.15);">
          <div class="dwh-card__icon" style="border:1px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.25);">
            <img src="/assets/img/intellica_camlogo_icibos.png" alt="" />
          </div>
          <h3>Cloud Modernization</h3>
          <p>Migration from on-premise to cloud-native architectures. Technology-agnostic approach across AWS, Azure, GCP.</p>
          <ul class="dwh-card__list">
            <li>Assessment & target architecture</li>
            <li>Phased migration approach</li>
            <li>Performance benchmarking</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="dwh-card" style="background:linear-gradient(145deg,#EFF6FF,#F0FDF9);border:1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.15);">
          <div class="dwh-card__icon" style="border:1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.25);">
            <img src="/assets/img/intellica_camlogo_icibos.png" alt="" />
          </div>
          <h3>Data Operations</h3>
          <p>Reliable data pipelines with quality gates, orchestration and observability.</p>
          <ul class="dwh-card__list">
            <li>ETL/ELT automation</li>
            <li>Data quality monitoring</li>
            <li>Alert & incident management</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="dwh-card" style="background:linear-gradient(145deg,#F5F3FF,#EFF6FF);border:1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.15);">
          <div class="dwh-card__icon" style="border:1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.25);">
            <img src="/assets/img/intellica_camlogo_icibos.png" alt="" />
          </div>
          <h3>Semantic Layer</h3>
          <p>Standardized business metrics, KPI governance and self-service BI enablement.</p>
          <ul class="dwh-card__list">
            <li>Metric standardization</li>
            <li>Self-service enablement</li>
            <li>Governed analytics</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section section--dark">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-strip anim-fade-up">
        <h2>Ready to <span class="grad-text">Transform</span>?</h2>
        <p>Let's discuss how our solutions can accelerate your data & AI maturity.</p>
        <a class="btn btn-primary btn-pill btn-lg" href="/contact">Schedule a Consultation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
.service-list {
  list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px;
}
.service-list li {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
  font-size: 0.88rem; color: #374151;
}
.service-list li::before {
  content: '';
  width: 6px; height: 6px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--grad-brand);
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.ai-portfolio-card__badge {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 4px 12px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  background: rgba(0,200,150,0.1);
  color: var(--clr-primary);
  border: 1px solid rgba(0,200,150,0.2);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.ai-portfolio-card h3 { margin-bottom: 12px; }
.ai-portfolio-card p { margin-bottom: 20px; }
.service-card { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
</style>
